data.description: Welcome Home! Welcome to this exquisite 4-bedroom, 2 1/2-bath residence, a splendid creation by the renowned Gray Point Homes (GEHAN). Step into a world of refined living as you explore the stunning interior. Wood flooring downstairs. Carpet in all of the bedrooms with tile in wet areas. Large laundry room just steps from the garage and the first floor also features a spacious study with double doors. Nestled amidst this inviting abode is a backyard haven, complete with a generous patio and charming gazebo.  This home is located minutes away from Randolph Air Force Base, Fort Sam Houston and The Forum. Easy access to 1604 and I-35. Easy commute to downtown San Antonio, Converse, Seguin and Schertz. All the restaurants, shopping and entertainment you could ask for!! Your dream home awaits!!  Don't miss the opportunity to view this beautiful home firsthand. Its numerous upgrades and spacious layout make it an ideal choice for seeking comfort and style. Visit and envision the possibilities of making it your own.    OPEN HOUSE!!   THIS SATURDAY 12/2 11-1PM
